| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-0488 — Recovery Inhibition (dispossessor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3f49285f-3abd-5e33-b636-7b43c8beaf92"
